    <span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px">1、杭州税牛有义务保证遵守本</span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">协议、《</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">易起名智慧起名</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务协议》及各项规范、规则的</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">正常使用</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务，当出现技术故障影响</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务的正常提供时，杭州税牛应尽快排除故障。</span></span>
</p>
<p>
