</p>
<p>
    <span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px">7、如</span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">在使用</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">易起名智慧起名</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务的过程中，存在违反法律法规的行为，杭州税牛有权取消该</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">的</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">资格而无须给予任何补偿，且该</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">服务</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">须自行承担全部责任。</span></span>
